      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "March 13, 1961",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Edgar J. Hoover",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Director",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Federal Bureau of Investigation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Hoover;",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "On March 1, 1961, I subscribed for a one year membership ($5.00)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "to \"The U.F.O. Investigator,\" published by the National Investigation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Committee on Aerial Phenomena - NICAP. This organization is located at:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "1536 Connecticut Avenue, N. W., Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "Today, I received acknowledgement of membership and my first",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "issue of \"U.F.O. Investigator.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "The contents of this issue points up the pressure being applied",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "to the United States Air Force, Congressional leaders and others to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "divulge secret information regarding Flying Saucers, etc.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "If our Air Force (or any other agency) has such information",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "and our government desires to keep same secret in the interest of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "national security, I would appreciate your answering this question",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "for me.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "\"IS NICAP a Communist sponsored outfit???",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "If so, I have inadvertantly contributed my name and support",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "to their cause, by my membership for one year.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Thank you for your interest and reply.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
